Copy applet-flash-samd51j18a.bin and mdloader_window.exe to qmk_firmware root.


Navigate to root of qmk_firmware folder and run the command MSYS2 to build:
make massdrop/ctrl:default

Navigate to root of qmk_firmware folder and run the command in command prompt:
mdloader_windows.exe --first --download massdrop_ctrl_default.bin --restart

make massdrop_custom/ctrl:default_custom
mdloader_windows.exe --first --download massdrop_custom_ctrl_default_custom.bin --restart